<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[الكُتْبة]</span>: الخُرْزة،<span class="c5"> والجمع:</span> كُتَب.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
